title: Can we help you find your next home? 1x1 ,2x1 and 2x2.  Waiting list
posting_body: ['Thank you for your interest in Brookhaven Apartments Homes!', '1x1, 2x1 and 2x2 Apartment Homes in a great location.', 'Talking names and number for waiting list.', 'Get on our waiting list now.', 'Access to everything you would need.', 'Features', '- Vertical blinds on patio door', '- Plush carpeting*', '- Each apartment home is fully equipped with a frost-free refrigerator, multi-cycle dishwasher and electric stove', '- Ceiling fans in dining rooms', '- Vaulted ceilings available*', '- Multiple telephone and electrical outlets', '- Cozy linen closets', '- High-Speed Internet access', '- Full-sized washer and dryer in every apartment home', '- Designer paint and color schemes*', '- Pre', '-wired for cable television in living rooms and', 'all bedrooms', '- Wood burning fireplaces with mantles and tile accents', '- Individual water heaters', '- Balconies or patios', '- Spacious walk-in closets*', '- Spacious pantries', '- Double stainless-steel sinks with disposals*', '- Faux granite counter tops in kitchens and baths*', '- Expansive bay windows*', 'Community Amenities', '- 3 blocks to Steel Lake Park', '- Walking distance to shopping', '- Proximity to bus line', '- Close to schools', '- Reserved car space for each apartment Home', '- Qualified pets welcome (weight and breed restriction)', '- 24-hour professional management', 'Pet Policy', '$500 ($250 non-refundable) per pet', 'Monthly pet rent $25 per pet per month', '2 pets maximum per apartment home', 'Weight limit is 35 lbs.', 'full grown', 'For further details, please contact the leasing office', 'Office Hours', 'Monday- Friday 8AM to 5PM']
